## Early game

Entrati Lanthorn is a **Zariman mission reward** from **Halako Perimeter**
(Extermination), and also shows up as a **bounty reward** on both the
Zariman and Deimos's **Cambion Drift**. Running Halako Perimeter
Extermination gives you a shot at its end-of-mission reward-table roll (about
9.76%), while rotating through a few Entrati or Zariman bounty stages tends
to net a Lanthorn or two per bounty chain.

Both sources are fixed reward-table rolls (mission-end and bounty-completion
rewards), not in-mission resource pickups, so **Resource Drop Boosters don't
affect Entrati Lanthorn from either source**.

## Mid & late game

Once you're deep into Entrati and Holdfast crafting, alternate between
**Halako Perimeter Extermination** runs and stacking **Cambion Drift /
Zariman bounties** back-to-back for their Lanthorn reward slots. Since
neither source is booster-affected, the efficient late-game loop is simply
to run more missions and bounty chains rather than saving boosters for this
resource.

